    <content>&lt;P&gt;It's been a while since I've interviewed.&amp;nbsp; Usually if I participate in an interview it is for a position I know I am a good fit for so the responses were positive.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;For the job I didn't get an offer for, the interviewer was honest at the time and said I didn't have a great deal of XML experience, which was required.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
