    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;I would take advantage of all the free training at learning.sap.com and then decide from there.&amp;nbsp; BTP is hot, along with the SAP Cloud products such as SAP Ariba and SAP Service Cloud.&amp;nbsp; Admin roles are very important in Cloud products.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;In terms of product management, have you taken the free SAP Activate training at learning.sap.com?&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://learning.sap.com/learning-journeys/discovering-sap-activate-implementation-tools-and-methodology" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://learning.sap.com/learning-journeys/discovering-sap-activate-implementation-tools-and-methodology&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
